1. Ona je odlučila da prihvati *ponudu* (She decided to accept the offer). 
2. Ona je odbila *ponudu* (She rejected the offer). 
3. On je ponudio da ode sa njom (He offered to go with her). 
4. Ona je ponudila novu ideju (She offered a new idea). 
5. Njegova *ponuda* je bila prihvaćena (His offer was accepted).